      <title>地方检察官告诉法官，特朗普封口费罪名必须维持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/trump-s-hush-money-conviction-must-be-preserved-da-tells-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼哈顿地区检察官阿尔文布拉格告诉法官，唐纳德特朗普在纽约封口费案中的刑事定罪不能因其选举胜利而撤销，而必须在他即将担任总统期间保留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/trump-s-hush-money-conviction-must-be-preserved-da-tells-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院共和党领袖米奇·麦康奈尔在跌倒后“恢复正常”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/mcconnell-fine-after-medical-personnel-enter-his-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院共和党领袖米奇·麦康奈尔周二摔倒并割伤了脸部，但一位同事表示，他在接受医疗救治后“没事”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/mcconnell-fine-after-medical-personnel-enter-his-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:37:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言为在美国投资 10 亿美元的企业快速发放许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/trump-expedited-permits-for-anyone-investing-1b-or-more-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他的政府将帮助任何在美国投资至少 10 亿美元的个人或公司加快办理许可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/trump-expedited-permits-for-anyone-investing-1b-or-more-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:21:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政治风暴加剧商业前景不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/french-economy-latest-political-storm-makes-business-uncertain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政局动荡导致工业和建筑业的不确定性达到2022年能源危机以来的最高水平，给该国的经济前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/french-economy-latest-political-storm-makes-business-uncertain</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登为经济纪录辩护，称特朗普计划威胁经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-defends-economic-record-says-trump-plans-threaten-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登警告称，共和党人唐纳德·特朗普延长减税并通过关税重塑全球贸易的计划可能会逆转经济增长，尽管对他自己对经济处理的不满导致了上个月惨痛的选举失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/biden-defends-economic-record-says-trump-plans-threaten-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:44:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>二十国集团谈判代表支持南非努力解决非洲大陆债务问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/g-20-sherpas-back-south-africa-s-push-to-tackle-continent-s-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界最大经济体的谈判代表达成广泛共识，支持南非的 G20 优先事项，包括解决非洲国家令人担忧的高债务问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/g-20-sherpas-back-south-africa-s-push-to-tackle-continent-s-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:43:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称更多爱国者防空系统可能改变战争进程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/zelenskiy-says-more-patriot-systems-could-change-course-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基在基辅对记者表示，另外 10 到 12 套美国制造的爱国者防空系统可以帮助乌克兰确保其领空安全，并改变俄罗斯对乌克兰战争的力量平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/zelenskiy-says-more-patriot-systems-could-change-course-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 18:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美光获 62 亿美元芯片订单，以刺激工厂扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/micron-gets-6-2-billion-chips-award-to-spur-plant-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府已达成最终协议，将从旨在促进美国半导体制造业发展的计划中向美光公司提供近 62 亿美元的补贴，使资金开始流向爱达荷州和纽约州的工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/micron-gets-6-2-billion-chips-award-to-spur-plant-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弗里兰称加拿大将实现债务目标，但对赤字保持沉默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chrystia-freeland-says-canada-to-meet-debt-goal-stays-quiet-on-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长克里斯蒂亚弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 表示，政府将继续实现逐步降低债务与国内生产总值比率的目标，但回避了有关预算赤字规模的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chrystia-freeland-says-canada-to-meet-debt-goal-stays-quiet-on-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强空袭并派遣军队深入叙利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/israel-steps-up-airstrikes-on-military-sites-in-syria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列加强了对叙利亚军事基地的袭击，袭击了从机场到武器生产基地的数百个目标，并派遣军队深入叙利亚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/israel-steps-up-airstrikes-on-military-sites-in-syria</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:32:41 GMT</pubDate>
